{"tid":2308592,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB「狂野港姐」廖慧儀前男友疑情困墮樓亡 胞妹：已經不在了","createTime":"2020-12-02T04:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T04:26:06.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0559053d323868fd115aea5daf75c0489228f60","tid":2308592,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"有「狂野港姐」之稱的廖慧儀自從入行後，與圈外男友Sam感情隨即出現問題，有指大台藝人孔德賢介入戀情，廖慧儀不久即狠飛阿Sam。分手情侶原本各行各路，但廖慧儀期後在IG透露自己被跟蹤、威脅、恐嚇，更試過被人當街搶電話，就連家人和朋友同告受害，直指「日日都玩跳樓，你要搞清楚呢啲唔係愛嘅表現。」誰知廖慧儀此句說話卻一語成讖。Sam胞妹在哥哥IG Story留言：「哥哥已經不在了，感謝你們的擔心，未來會有設靈，會再通知。」記者致電廖慧儀，問到知唔知Sam出事？她說：「唔得閒，唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n今日早上6時許，一名27歲姓張男子，從油麻地一大廈高處墮下，救護員趕至現場，將傷者送往廣華醫院搶救，惟終告不治。有指死者是廖慧儀舊愛Sam，而他在墮樓前半小時內，在IG留言尋死，用英文寫：Thank you for everyone who have been supporting throughout my journey.Goodbye.Please forgive me for doing this.Been suffering for 2 months both mentally and physically.Just couldn&rsquo;t take it any longer.Sorry（感謝所有在我人生路上幫助過我的人。再見！原諒我這樣做。精神和身體上受折磨兩個月）<br />\n<br />\n廖慧儀原本和Sam愛得甜蜜，二人過往在IG經常貼出拍拖相，可是，之後有傳廖慧儀與無綫節目《#後生仔傾吓偈》的23歲大學KOL孔德賢（Danny）撻着，Sam盛怒下於IG上公開警告Danny不要找他女友，可惜激烈行為依舊挽回不到這段感情。原本網民一直同情Sam遭遇，但自從廖慧儀爆出男方做出連番過激行為後，不少網民留言都轉鬧男方，指他分手後騷擾女友和家人，連基本尊重都不懂，亦有人留言叫他振作，不要為一個女人而自毁前程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201202/MYUME6Y2ANFCZGRVQCXB6UZFFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201202%2FMYUME6Y2ANFCZGRVQCXB6UZFFA%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2e6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=2936629e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201202%2FMYUME6Y2ANFCZGRVQCXB6UZFFA%2F&h=5587bafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201202/MYUME6Y2ANFCZGRVQCXB6UZFFA/</a>"},{"pid":"c14f7c1af585865498ea75fcbc195adc2230365d","tid":2308592,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200625/WVG5LNPZJ34ZPKVJLQDCXN4QOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200625%2FWVG5LNPZJ34ZPKVJLQDCXN4QOQ%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2e6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=6474b1a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200625%2FWVG5LNPZJ34ZPKVJLQDCXN4QOQ%2F&h=244e816b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200625/WVG5LNPZJ34ZPKVJLQDCXN4QOQ/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089dd45f047b74a9ffbf88586fb5c95af0e2af35","tid":2308592,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"入得tvb 做既唔方好人 早飛早著何必跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d0c3536aacd11e75e4ce0ea509b9e6fbcfe716","tid":2308592,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"東將幾時去訪問條女?"},{"pid":"1b80b87a20e4ae30142107830a193e87be5ad169","tid":2308592,"uid":160555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"肯定係比人日日恥笑綠帽慘執"},{"pid":"faaffbaf32d60639bdfa4e370e34cd990c1ec242","tid":2308592,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://storage.inewsdb.com/c7fbf0ab22599bfc125894295d30c8c7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.inewsdb.com%2Fc7fbf0ab22599bfc125894295d30c8c7.jpeg&h=dcc9154f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f36d87c9ff03f949d3751f429b119e2723865c31","tid":2308592,"uid":36049,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"Danny Hung 呢條含家產究竟害死左幾多條人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdcb899d1679bc5e64d0f33f8fea4ffbce